window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The second original novel in an Alien vs. Predator: Rage War series, continuing from <i>Predator: Incursion</i> as Colonial Marines units are being wiped out - and not by the Predators. This is an attack by organized armies of Aliens. </p> <p>Tim Lebbon is the <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author of the movie novelizations of <i>30 Days of Night</i> and <i>The Cabin in the Woods</i>. He has also written many critically acclaimed horror and dark fantasy novels. Tim has won three British Fantasy Awards, a Bram Stoker Award, a Shocker, and a Tombstone and been a finalist for the International Horror Guild and World Fantasy Awards. </p>"; 
